data.description: Golf Course View!!!!  Lovely 2 story home that is located in Oxford & Cider Ridge Subdivision!  This home features 5 bedrooms ( 3 master suites-1 master down), formal living room, formal dining room,  family room w/fireplace, kitchen w/breakfast area/island/bar, laundry room and a double garage. Amenities are endless and include hardwood floors, ceramic tile, granite countertops, walk-in shower and jetted tub, crown molding, trey & vaulted ceilings, can lights, walk-in closets, sitting area in master ensuite, pantry, tile shower, full brick exterior, surround sound, columns, archways, stainless appliances, tile backsplash, iron staircase,  screened porch, and lavish landscaping and so much more. The outside offers a golf course view and privacy. Don't miss out on this opportunity of home ownership, A place for the whole family to play as it offers golf, swimming, tennis and much more. Seeing is believing!!!
